        "short_description": "Rec Room is the best place to build and play games together. Party up with friends from all around the world to chat, hang out, explore MILLIONS of player-created rooms, or build something new and amazing to share with us all.",
        "detailed_description": "Rec Room is the best place to build and play games together. Party up with friends from all around the world to chat, hang out, explore MILLIONS of player-created rooms, or build something new and amazing to share with us all.<br />\r\nRec Room is free, and cross plays on everything from phones to VR headsets. It’s the social app you play like a video game!<br />\r\n- Customize and dress up your cute Rec Room avatar to express your style<br />\r\n- Discover challenging, fun or straight up weird games made by creators just like you<br />\r\n- Try your skill with the Maker Pen, the tool used by Rec Room creators to build everything from puppies to helicopters to entire worlds!<br />\r\n- Join the best community - Rec Room is a fun and welcoming place for people from all walks of life! Let us help you find people you’ll LOVE to hang out with.",
